Key Design Principles of This Expansion

Your transcriber is treated as a black box — SVC-10 only requires transcribe(url, start, end) → str. Swap it for a better model anytime with zero changes elsewhere.
The summary fallback is non-disruptive — it only fires above a measured threshold, never on the first signal. Learners are not interrupted unnecessarily.
All video data flows through the same Data Store and Learner Profiler — so a learner who watches a video and then returns to text gets a unified adaptive experience.

